name: o11.1 — Leave the darkness alone — rev.01.1
description: On the way of spiritual emancipation, everyone has the right and the opportunity to go faster than others. On this road, there are no such obstacles as exist in the material world where there is dependence on each other.  At the same time, many forward-looking people are displeased. They do not understand that the fear of being late and the fear that someone is better than them makes them hurry. Those in a hurry become superficial and begin to make mistakes. Fear obscures the mind.
